{"tid":1679194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位準備好持久戰未？","createTime":"2019-10-28T05:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T08:40:44.000Z","uid":185158,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"718d2114b1f10cbb97d453b6f6c71fe6d7e63bf5","tid":1679194,"uid":185158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:13:00.000Z","msg":"香港人成日比人串急功近利<br />\n搵快錢至上<br />\n但係<br />\n今次時代革命<br />\n我地挑戰緊世上最大既極權國家<br />\n唔好比伊拉克，印尼，智利既成功影響左<br />\n覺得人地咁短時間就得，點解香港唔得<br />\n記住，「我地挑戰緊世上最大既極權國家」<br />\n<br />\n各位手足<br />\n問下自己<br />\n有無積極投入黃色經濟圈既建設<br />\n有無保持傳播文宣既狀態<br />\n有無最少出席一下拎到不反對通知書既集會<br />\n<br />\n堅持，反抗<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"4fd00b94b42dd96e35111679b5c38b17f90ed9dc","tid":1679194,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:13:18.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c64a23f25dadc749699d83c4c9c657ee131cf07","tid":1679194,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽 5毛大軍不代表香港人<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD584e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=01f7dfca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"a2d1ad3e7b3fe33b9905f88a9d92d85e015eb0c4","tid":1679194,"uid":185158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:14:26.000Z","msg":"唔好睇小自己既力量！星星之火 可以燎原"},{"pid":"8f66f4c917b446e2b28cca458059d63fe4b51486","t